SIMPLE: swearer
RECORDS: 1

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Swearer
<hw>Swear"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
swears; one who calls God to witness for the truth of his
declaration.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A profane person; one who uses profane
language.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Then the liars and <qex>swearers</qex> are fools.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Swearing</ent>⟦br⟧
